graph LR
    LlamaOperator[Llama Stack Operator<br/>v0.6.0]

    %% External Dependencies
    LlamaOperator -->|runtime platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.20+]
    LlamaOperator -->|operator framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime<br/>v0.22.4]
    LlamaOperator -->|manifest templating| Kustomize[kustomize v0.21.0]
    LlamaOperator -.->|optional metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    LlamaOperator -.->|optional external access| IngressController[Ingress Controller]

    %% Inference Provider Dependencies
    LlamaOperator -->|creates deployments using| Ollama[Ollama<br/>11434/TCP HTTP]
    LlamaOperator -->|creates deployments using| vLLM[vLLM<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    LlamaOperator -->|TLS certificates| CABundle[odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap]
    LlamaOperator -.->|optional networking| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|future UI mgmt| LlamaOperator
    LlamaOperator -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% External Services
    LlamaOperator -->|distribution images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    vLLM -->|model downloads| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Managed Resources
    LlamaOperator -->|creates/manages| LlamaStack[Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
    LlamaOperator -->|creates/manages| CRD[LlamaStackDistribution CRD<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
    LlamaOperator -->|creates/manages| NetPol[NetworkPolicy<br/>feature flag]
    LlamaOperator -->|creates/manages| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>10Gi default]

    %% Prometheus integration
    PrometheusOp -->|scrapes| LlamaOperator

    %% Styling
    style LlamaOperator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (required)
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Kustomize fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (optional)
    style PrometheusOp fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style IngressController fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Inference providers
    style Ollama fill:#cc9900,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style vLLM fill:#cc9900,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH (required)
